Package uk.ac.cf.milling.objects

Class KPIs

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.cf.milling.objects.KPIs
public class KPIs extends Object
Holds values for virtual process KPIs and temporary stores simulation run
information that is required to do the simulation and report results.
Author:
Theocharis Alexopoulos
